         race is available in William H. P. Robertson, 
         <title xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:type="simple" render="italic" xlink:href="">The History of Thoroughbred Racing In
         America</title>(Englewood Cliffs, New Jersey: Prentice-Hall,
         Inc., 1964), 304-305, Rare Books, Scott SF335.U5R6 1964.</p>
    </descgrp>
